result.title: TVSS Flag Football Team Registration (up to 16 people)

group.description:
This group is perfect for active, fun people who want to be social and enjoy a variety of activities. Expect variety, such as kickball, pickleball, soccer, cornhole, beach volleyball, dodgeball, tennis, badminton, foot golf, greenbelt bike rides, hikes, Texas Hold'em poker, coffee or happy hours, outdoor restaurant visits/cultural activities, etc. 
Minimum age group requirement is 21; the group leaders take no responsibility or no liability for your personal safety.
All cultural backgrounds are respected. 
We thank our sponsors since 5/6/2022: Treasure Valley Sports Leagues (treasurevalleysportsleagues.com)!
See you soon!
As a standard policy, if a new member does not show up within two months of joining, he/she may be dropped as a member. Thank you for understanding that we like to protect our group's integrity as much as possible.
NOTE: As COVID-19 continues to seriously impact our community, for this group, mask wearing or not will not be a debate; if the event requires a mask it will say it and the expectation is that you will be respectful of that. THANK YOU!
group.name: Treasure Valley Sports and Social Club (TVSS)

FIFA 20 - Xbox/PS4

group.description:
Welcome to the Sports Monster Denver Flag Football Group!

Our goal is to create a fun, social environment where football enthusiasts or men & women just looking to stay active can have some fun tossing the pigskin around.

You can participate in the following:

8-week leagues with scheduled opponents each week, all equipment provided, standings, and a playoff tournament
One-day tournaments
Pickup nights where players can come out each week and get in a few games without the commitment of a full league
College and professional watch parties, and more
Feel free to RSVP for as much football action as you'd like and if you have any questions don't hesitate to email me: mattv@sportsmonster.net. I'd love to hear from you!
group.name: Sports Monster Denver Flag Football Group
